{
  "chapter": 237,
  "chapter_summary": "本章分两条线索展开。寇仲在梁都书斋研读机关秘本时，任媚媚来访投怀送抱，被寇仲以修练长生诀为由婉拒。随后杨虚彦黑衣蒙面行刺寇仲，两人激战数十回合，杨虚彦见惊动众人后撤退，寇仲负伤但仍稳住局面。宣永、陈家风等将领赶来商议防卫对策，寇仲决定全城通缉杨虚彦并加强府内暗哨。与此同时，徐子陵扮成岳山随石青璇进入伏魔洞。石青璇揭穿徐子陵身份，透露收到鲁妙子临终密函。尤鸟倦、丁九重、周老叹、金环真四名邪派高手追入洞中欲夺邪帝舍利。石青璇利用洞中千万蝙蝠设下陷阱，与徐子陵联手准备伏击四人。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "笃！笃！笃！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 3,
      "line_end": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ren_mei_mei",
      "text": "任大姐请进来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 5,
      "line_end": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "任媚媚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "少帅怎知是人家来呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ren_mei_mei",
      "text": "任何人的足音，只要给我记牢，便不会忘记。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "任媚媚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我的足音难道时常保持不变吗？例如人家刚才来时，尽量放轻脚步，原想吓你一跳哩！",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ren_mei_mei",
      "text": "足音除可快慢轻重不同外，还会随心情生出变化，但无论如何改变，总保留其中某些不变的音韵，就像每个人走路的姿态亦有分异，只是一般人不留意吧！所以当我和小陵易容改装作别人的身份时，会更改行止坐卧的形韵姿态，以免露出破绽，说来容易，但做起来真的非常辛苦和吃力。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "任媚媚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "哎哟！谁想得到其中竟有这么大的学问，这究竟是怎么学来的？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ren_mei_mei",
      "text": "是这个家伙自己想出来的，这叫自食其力嘛。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 27,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "任媚媚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "当年在赌场初遇，你两个只是黄毛小子，一副手颤脚震，战战兢兢模样，岂知数年之间，摇身一变而成叱吒风云的年青俊彦，姐姐也当了你的小卒子，当初怎么想得到。",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ren_mei_mei",
      "text": "巴陵帮在这一带是否仍有势力？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "任媚媚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "明的都给徐圆朗拔掉，暗里尚有三、四家妓院，只要你一句话，我可把它们连根拔起。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ren_mei_mei",
      "text": "现在尚未是时候。嘻嘻！任大姐来找小弟，有甚么特别的事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "任媚媚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "定要有事才可找你吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ren_mei_mei",
      "text": "我还以为任大姐历经变乱，已收心养性，原来仍是以前那副风流性子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "任媚媚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "人家是欢喜你嘛！且你正值壮年，总要女人来侍候枕席，不如让姐姐悉心侍奉，保君满意。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ren_mei_mei",
      "text": "我也知道大姐会令我非常满意，但我正害怕因太过满意而乐而忘返。由于我练的是来自道家的长生诀，不宜纵欲，际此开基创业的初期，更须克制。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "任媚媚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "人家陪你一晚该没问题吧？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ren_mei_mei",
      "text": "大姐太低估自己对我的诱惑力，只要有一晚，将会有第二晚和第三晚，不若亲亲你的甜嘴儿算啦！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "任媚媚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你想引死人吗？不过就算给你拒绝，人家心中仍是很高兴的。以前大当家就是因过份沉溺美色，致功力减退，否则不会内伤不愈而死。所以人家虽有点恨你，但也心中佩服，这感觉真矛盾。",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ren_mei_mei",
      "text": "不要恨我，保持亲热的姐弟之情，会比男女肉体的快乐更恒久和动人。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "任媚媚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "到现在姐姐才明白做大事的人是怎样子的。难怪你能冒升得这么快！好啦！人家不打扰你了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "任媚媚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "陪你过夜未必需有交欢的，搂着人家睡觉也挺舒服哩！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ren_mei_mei",
      "text": "搂着一团火还如何睡觉？差点忘记告诉你，我睡觉的时候，就是练功的时刻。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "进来！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_yang_xu_yan",
      "text": "小子知道厉害吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_xu_yan",
      "speaker_name": "杨虚彦",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "今天算你走运！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好家伙，差点给你成功了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "欢迎到伏魔洞来！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "text": "这是甚么一回事？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我本想凭一己之力收拾这四个凶邪，现在多你帮手，自然更有把握。你究竟是徐子陵还是寇仲？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "text": "甚么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "若非从岳山的面具猜到你是谁，我怎肯把你带到这里来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "text": "你就算看出这是岳山的假面具，但又从何可猜到我是徐子陵？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "道理很简单，因为我收到鲁先生仙去前寄出的密函，知道你们和鲁先生的关系。而且我是亲眼目睹岳山的逝世，所以绝不会误认你是真的岳山，更知道你是非徐即寇。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "text": "原来给人揭破身份，感觉是这么尴尬兼窝囊的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "现在我完全放心了！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "text": "你从未见过我，为何只瞧几眼便完全放心，我仍可以不是徐子陵的。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我擅长脸相观人之术，故知你不是奸妄之徒，大可以放心。就算你不是徐子陵，也绝非坏人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_niao_juan",
      "speaker_name": "尤鸟倦",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "text": "石小姐姑奶奶小贱人，你若不给我滚出来，要劳烦我下来找你，我会教你求生不得，求死不能。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_lao_tan",
      "speaker_name": "周老叹",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "text": "小贱人竟敢拿假舍利来骗我们，真舍利究竟在那里？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_you_niao_juan",
      "text": "真正的邪帝舍利当然在我这里，有本事下来拿吧！我要走了！",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "任媚媚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "来的是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ren_mei_mei",
      "text": "是杨虚彦那小子！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yong",
      "speaker_name": "宣永",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我们要加强总管府的防卫才成。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yong",
      "text": "此人的行刺方式层出不穷，且可在任何地方进行，不用为他一人浪费精神人力。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jia_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陈家风",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "那怎办才好？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_chen_jia_feng",
      "text": "我并不怕他，只是怕他摸清我们底子后，把刺杀目标转移到你们身上，以打击我们的士气、信心，削弱我们的实力。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yong",
      "speaker_name": "宣永",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这事确非常棘手，唯一方法是设法把他找出来，至少要把他赶离梁都，否则人人睡难安寝。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yong",
      "text": "这虽然非是易事，却不是全无方法办到，由于他的体型特别，易于辨认，所以只要通告全城军民，留意这么一号人物，他将难以藏身。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ren_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "任媚媚",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "说不定他仍留在总管府内等待机会？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_ren_mei_mei",
      "text": "我们费点功夫，先搜查总管府，肯定他不在这里后，再在府内设置暗哨，拟定一套有效的警报方法，至少令敌人不会如入无人之境。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yong",
      "speaker_name": "宣永",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "假设他真的仍在府中，我们…",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yong",
      "text": "若是如此，便轮到我刺杀他哩！哈！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "不要高声说话，下面住了以千万计的蝙蝠，一旦把它们惊动，那情景会把人骇死。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你知否为何刚才路经的各洞没有蝙蝠呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "因为那里有种怪石，是蝙蝠的克星，所以它们都不敢到那里去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我把那些怪石研成的粉末涂在你的头发上，蝙蝠便不敢飞近至你三尺范围之内，动手时将大大有利。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 331,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我们要把他们引进蝙蝠集中最多的洞穴，那时就是他们的死期到了，你负责动手，我则负责以箫音的波动驱使蝙蝠，明白吗？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "text": "一切谨依吩咐？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 341,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我要吹掉灯火！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你自行选择伏击的位置，这四人都是死有馀辜的奸邪，杀一个世人会活得安乐一点，下手绝不可留情。若你不幸战死，我会发动机关，封闭所有出口，和他们来个同归于尽，为你报仇。记着，我会为你营造偷袭的机会。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 365,
      "line_end": 369
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "text": "姑娘长得真美，在下定不负所托。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 237,
      "line_start": 375,
      "line_end": 377
    }
  ],
